properties.name: Cliff Bentz
properties.biography: Bentz received a bachelor's degree in history from Eastern Oregon College in 1974 and a degree from Lewis and Clarke Law School in 1977. After finishing law school, he joined the firm of Yturri, O'Kief, Rose, and Burnham, where, as of the 2020 election cycle, he continued to work part-time as a senior partner.
